@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.01) - v2)
    v1 = v1
    tmp = 0.23
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.82)))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.53) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.11)) + wp.sin((v0 + 0.11 * v0 + 0.63)))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.72) / v1) - wp.sin(wp.exp(v0 + 0.92)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.14 - tmp + 0.40)) + (wp.abs(tmp + 0.70) * 0.75))
    data[tid] = v0
